author: COMSOL
description: This model demonstrates how to extend the built-in linear elastic material model to a Cosserat elastic material through the addition of the microrotation degrees of freedom. A cylindrical bar under pure torsion is analyzed and the effect of the Cosserat length scale parameter on the response is observed.
